#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:44
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kbruch; is a small program to practice calculating with fractions. "
#| "Different exercises are provided for this purpose. The program checks "
#| "user's input and gives feedback."
msgid ""
"&kbruch; is a small program to practice calculating with fractions and "
"percentages. Different exercises are provided for this purpose and you can "
"use the learning mode to practice with fractions. The program checks the "
"user's input and gives feedback."
msgstr ""
"&kbruch; er et lille program beregnet til at øve sig i at regne med brøker. "
"Der sørges for forskellige øvelser til dette formål. Programmet tjekker det "
"brugeren skriver og giver en tilbagemelding."

